textBox.richText: In Between The Lines + Midnight Ramblers = a) In Between The Midnight Lines b) Rambling Between The Lines c) In Between The Ramblers d) In Between The Notes e) Midnight Between The Lines Have you ever wondered what voice part your favorite improviser sings? Do the Ramblers make stuff up as they go along? Can two groups combine to make performance history? These questions, and many others, will be answered at this show. Yes, that's right. The Midnight Ramblers' a cappella meets In Between The Lines' improv to bring you a one of a kind musical comedy experience. It's free, but seats will go fast.
In Between the Lines & Midnight Ramblers Joint Show
